---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import CTASection from "../components/CTASection.astro";
import FAQ from "../components/FAQ.astro";
import PlatformShowcase from "../components/PlatformShowcase.astro";

const title = "Email Marketing Platform & Systems for Developers | Laravel Mail";
const description = "Discover the ultimate email marketing platform for technical teams. Master email growth, automation, and deliverability with Laravel Mail's self-hosted software.";
const keywords = "email marketing, laravel email marketing platform, email marketing software, automated email marketing, laravel mail, email marketing for small business, laravel email campaigns, laravel mail queue, laravel transactional email, self hosted email marketing platform";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} keywords={keywords}>
    <section class="pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-28 md:pb-24 overflow-hidden relative">
        <div class="container-custom relative">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-brand-primary/10 border border-brand-primary/20 text-brand-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">
                    Pillar Page
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black leading-tight text-white mb-8">
                    Email Marketing Platform <br/><span class="gradient-text">for Developers</span>
                </h1>
                    <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-10">
                        Step into the future of <strong>email marketing</strong>. Whether you're an indie hacker or an enterprise team, 
                        our <strong>laravel email marketing platform</strong> is designed to scale your <strong>email marketing systems</strong> 
                        and deliver high-performing <strong>laravel email campaigns</strong> with native <strong>laravel mail queue</strong> support.
                    </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
                    <a href="/install" class="btn btn-primary px-8 py-4 text-lg">Get Started with Laravel Mail</a>
                    <a href="#overview" class="text-white hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors font-medium">Explore the Systems ↓</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="overview" class="py-20 bg-brand-bg/50">
        <div class="container-custom">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">What is the Modern Email Marketing Platform?</h2>
                    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-300">
                        <p>
                            A modern <strong>laravel email marketing platform</strong> is more than just a sender; it's a core component of your 
                            product's communication layer. In today's landscape, <strong>email marketing software</strong> must be 
                            high-performance, developer-friendly, and privacy-first. With native support for <strong>laravel mail</strong> 
                            and <strong>laravel email templates</strong>, our platform integrates seamlessly into your existing stack.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            For growing businesses, <strong>email marketing for small business</strong> often means juggling expensive 
                            SaaS costs. Our <strong>self hosted email marketing platform</strong> redefines this by providing professional <strong>email marketing systems</strong> 
                            that you own. This allows you to scale your <strong>laravel email campaigns</strong> without 
                            paying a "subscriber tax."
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            We view <strong>email marketing</strong> as a technical challenge that deserves a technical solution. 
                            By using our <strong>open source email marketing software</strong>, you gain absolute control over your 
                            deliverability, data, and user experience. Every <strong>laravel transactional email</strong> and marketing message 
                            stays within your infrastructure.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-brand-primary/5 border border-brand-primary/20 rounded-2xl p-8">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Core Email Marketing Pillars</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold">01.</span>
                            <span><strong>Laravel Mail:</strong> Native integration with <strong>laravel mail queue</strong>, mailables, and notifications for transactional and marketing email.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold">02.</span>
                            <span><strong>Automated Email Marketing:</strong> Building smart, event-driven communication flows with <strong>laravel marketing automation</strong>.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold">03.</span>
                            <span><strong>Deliverability:</strong> Ensuring your <strong>laravel email campaigns</strong> hit the inbox with proper SPF, DKIM, and DMARC.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold">04.</span>
                            <span><strong>Segmentation:</strong> Targeting the right users with <strong>laravel customer segmentation</strong> and <strong>email marketing systems</strong>.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20">
        <div class="container-custom text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Automation & Software Excellence</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                The best <strong>email marketing service</strong> is one that integrates seamlessly with your existing stack. 
                Automation is no longer a luxury—it's the engine of modern growth.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="container-custom">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-brand-primary/50 transition-all duration-300">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Laravel Native</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">
                        Built for <strong>laravel mail</strong> with native support for mailables, notifications, and <strong>laravel mail queue</strong> for high performance.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-brand-primary/50 transition-all duration-300">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Zero Contact Tax</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">
                        Scale your <strong>laravel email campaigns</strong> to millions of contacts without increasing costs. Unlimited subscribers at a flat rate.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-brand-primary/50 transition-all duration-300">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Total Ownership</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">
                        Your <strong>laravel transactional email</strong> infrastructure, your data, your rules. No shared IPs, no per-email fees, no SaaS gatekeepers.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-brand-primary/5 relative">
        <div class="container-custom">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                 <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div class="p-6 bg-brand-bg border border-white/10 rounded-xl text-center">
                            <span class="block text-4xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">10M+</span>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Monthly Emails</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-6 bg-brand-bg border border-white/10 rounded-xl text-center">
                            <span class="block text-4xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">99%</span>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Inbound Reputation</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-6 bg-brand-bg border border-white/10 rounded-xl text-center">
                            <span class="block text-4xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">∞</span>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Subscriber Growth</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-6 bg-brand-bg border border-white/10 rounded-xl text-center">
                            <span class="block text-4xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">100%</span>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Data Sovereignty</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Systems Built for Laravel Developers</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 font-medium">
                        Laravel is the perfect ecosystem for building world-class <strong>laravel email marketing platform</strong>. 
                        Our <strong>email marketing software</strong> leverages the power of Eloquent, Queues, and Notifications 
                        to deliver a premium <strong>laravel email automation system</strong> with <strong>laravel email templates</strong> 
                        and <strong>laravel mail queue</strong> performance.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-400">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                             <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                             Full control over your <strong>laravel email campaigns</strong> triggers, timing, and segmentation.
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                             <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                             Supports advanced <strong>laravel marketing automation</strong> with multi-stage drips and behavioral triggers.
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                             <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                             Detailed <strong>laravel email analytics</strong> and reporting for every campaign and transactional message.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <PlatformShowcase />

    <FAQ />

    <section class="py-20">
        <div class="container-custom">
            <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-400 text-sm">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-4">Deep Dive: Master Your Email Marketing Software</h2>
                <p>
                     To truly excel in <strong>email marketing</strong>, one must understand the underlying <strong>email systems</strong>. 
                     For Laravel developers, this means leveraging <strong>laravel mail</strong>, <strong>laravel mail queue</strong>, 
                     and <strong>laravel email templates</strong> to build sophisticated <strong>laravel email campaigns</strong>. 
                     This transition is made possible by high-quality <strong>email marketing software</strong> that puts the developer in charge.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Every <strong>laravel email campaign</strong> you send is an opportunity to learn about your audience. 
                    By using advanced <strong>laravel email analytics</strong> and <strong>laravel email tracking</strong>, you can perform deep-dive analysis on your 
                    <strong>laravel transactional email</strong> performance. From subject line optimization to send-time analysis, 
                    the right <strong>laravel email marketing platform</strong> makes data actionable.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The future of <strong>email marketing</strong> is self-hosted. As third-party data becomes more restricted, 
                    owning your <strong>laravel email automation system</strong> becomes a massive competitive advantage. 
                    By building your <strong>laravel marketing automation</strong> on our <strong>self hosted email marketing platform</strong>, you ensure that your 
                    <strong>open source email marketing software</strong> is future-proof and fully compliant with evolving standards.
                </p>
                
                <p>
                    A professional <strong>laravel email marketing platform</strong> is the lifeblood of any modern SaaS or e-commerce business. 
                    Without reliable <strong>email marketing software</strong>, user retention and growth become significantly more difficult. 
                    Our mission is to provide the best <strong>email marketing for small business</strong> and enterprise developers alike, 
                    ensuring that <strong>laravel email campaigns</strong> and <strong>laravel notification email</strong> is accessible and powerful for everyone.
                </p>
                <p>
                    When choosing an <strong>email marketing service</strong>, consider the long-term implications of data ownership. 
                    Shared <strong>email marketing systems</strong> can put your reputation at risk. 
                    With a dedicated <strong>laravel email marketing platform</strong>, you are the master of your <strong>laravel email campaigns</strong> 
                    destiny. Join the thousands of Laravel developers who have switched to a better way of doing <strong>email marketing</strong>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection />
</Layout>
